## Monorepo Setup Example

Here's how to structure oRPC in a monorepo:

```
/packages/
  /api-contract/          # Shared contract
    package.json
    src/
      index.ts            # Export contracts
      user.contract.ts
      post.contract.ts

  /api-server/            # Server implementation
    package.json
    src/
      index.ts            # HTTP handler
      routers/
        user.router.ts
        post.router.ts

  /api-client/            # Client package
    package.json
    src/
      index.ts            # Export typed client

/apps/
  /web/                   # Next.js app
    package.json
    app/
      providers.tsx       # TanStack Query setup
```

